{
  "texts": [
    "After analyzing their title and abstract, 59 papers were chosen for a more detailed analysis (stage 2).",
    "We selected 21 papers (stage 3) from this set to compose our study.",
    "Most of the 38 papers discarded during stage 3 are related to NLP (14 papers) and image-based (6 papers) applications in health.",
    "However, their approaches do not process longitudinal multifeature data.",
    "The next paragraphs discuss some of the discarded papers, emphasizing the rationale of our decisions and better characterizing the scope of this review."
  ]
}